data.title: Files List Authors
data.meta_description: Files List Authors - Free ebook download as Text File (.txt), PDF File (.pdf) or read book online for free. This document lists file paths for folders within a J:\LIBRARY directory on a system. It shows folders labeled with letters A-Z and some additional folders. Within each lettered folder are many additional subfolders named for authors with initials matching that letter. The file paths indicate over 500 total author subfolders under the library folders.
